Instructions:

Press down joystick once when "PLAY TAG" appears on the screen

Whoever of the two players presses this first, becomes player1

Move your pixel by pushing the joystick in the left, right, up and down positions

If you start the game as player1, you are initially the tagger, try to tag player2

Player2, attempt to evade player1

If you are tagged, the tagger becomes the taggee and vice versa

Have fun :)
